vista.set
Class MultiIterator

java.lang.Object
  vista.set.MultiIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, DataSetIterator
public class MultiIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataSetIterator

This is a multi time series iterator. Each element returned by this iterator is a time tuple that has the dimension == number of time series + 1. If a certain value in a time series is no existent at the time it is set to Float.NAN for the tuple that is returned by getElement()
